  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  African American

          -  Hypertension and one of the following:

          -  Fasting glucose &gt; 100 mg/dl

          -  HgA1C&gt; 6.0 %

          -  Plasma triglycerides &gt;150

          -  HDL cholesterol &lt; 40 mg/dl in men or &lt; 50 mg/dl in women

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of Heart failure

          -  use of insulin

          -  non-dominant arm circ &gt; 50 cm.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
